      <relatedmaterial>
         <head id="a5">RELATED MATERIALS</head>
         <p>See also collection #6695 Box 4 for some oversize items from NYWGG including advertising proofs for NY wine and grape campaigns.</p>
         <p>See also Cornell Cooperative Extension Finger Lakes Grape Program records, #6773.</p>
         <p>Forms part of the Eastern Wine and Grape Archive. (EWGA)</p>
      </relatedmaterial>
